<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Nassau-Wiesbaden-Ibstein, Erzbischof von Mainz, Johann II. von Brunn, Bischof von Würzburg, Friedrich VI. von Hohenzollern, Burggraf von Nürnberg, Leonhard, Graf von Castell, Konrad IV. Schenk von Limpurg, Johann II., Graf von Wertheim, Thomas, Graf von Rieneck, Konrad IX. von Weinsberg, Konrad VI. von Bickenbach, Burggraf zu Miltenberg, Hanneman Echter von Mespelbrunn, Viztum zu Aschaffenburg, und Arnold von Seckendorff, Amtmann zu Neustadt an der Aisch</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit für Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute auf dem Weg zu und von der Frankfurter Fastenmesse.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_264" id="132r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_264_r1l3">Bẏſſchoff cʒu Meincʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l4">Bẏſſchoff cʒu <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l5"><expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wer <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l7">Graf <expan>Lynhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von Caſtell vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>Schenke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> von </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_264_r1l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu </ab></add> <expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l8">Graf <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> von wertheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l9">Graf Thomas von Ryneck </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l10"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu weinſperg Erb <expan>Camermeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l11"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>aden</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu Pickembach <expan>Burgr<ex>af</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Mıltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l12"><expan>ha<ex>n</ex>man</expan> Echter vicʒtume cʒu <expan>Aſcheffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l13"><expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Seckendorff Amptman cʒu der <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>ſtat</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="head"><ab facs="#facs_264_r1l1">Geleẏtbrief in die <expan>vaſte<ex>n</ex>meſſe</expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="content"><pb facs="#facs_264"/>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l14"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> VVir <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ ewr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l15"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute vnd auch Jr habe vnd kauffmanſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l16">vnd die Jren in die nehſtkünfftigen frankfurter vaſtenmeſſe / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l17">vvider darauſʒ . mit geleẏte <expan>gnedıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle / Alſo <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l18">oder die Jren / darümb cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden . oder aber den ~ ewren <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l19">vnd des bergern / daʒ ſie vnd daʒ Jr <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch ewr lande herſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l20">vnd gepyte ſicher geleytet werden / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc vnd biten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l21">auch des ewr gnedig <expan>vſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider beẏ <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l23"><expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan></del> in <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Mathie <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan> Anno xvȷ<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l24"><expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l25"><expan>no<ex>ta</ex></expan> <expan>officialib<ex>us</ex></expan> ſic </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l26"><expan>VVen<ex>n</ex></expan> ſie oder die Jren darümb cʒu euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l27">kumen vnd des begern daʒ Jr ſie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l28">durch ewr gepiete <expan>alſu<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Jr cʒugeleiten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_264_r1l29">habt ſicher geleẏten wöllet / Als etc Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab></note>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_264" id="132r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu Meincz<lb/>Bysschoff czu
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan><lb/><expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wer <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                        hat<lb/>Graf <expan>Lynhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von Castell und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Schenke<ex>n,</ex></expan>
<add><expan>h<ex>er</ex>re<ex>n</ex></expan> czu</add>
<expan>Lymp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan><lb/>Graf <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> von
                        Wertheim<lb/>Graf Thomas von Ryneck<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                        Weinsperg, erb<expan>camermeist<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                etc.<lb/><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>aden</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                        Pickembach, <expan>burgr<ex>af</ex></expan> czu
                            <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan><lb/>H<expan>a<ex>n</ex>man</expan>
                        Echter, vicztume czu
                                <expan>Ascheffemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan><lb/>A<expan>rnolt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von Seckendorff, amptman czu der <expan>Newe<ex>n</ex>stat</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="head"><ab>Geleytbrief in die <expan>vaste<ex>n</ex>messe</expan> </ab></div>
<div type="content"><ab><pb facs="#facs_264"/>
<expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ewr gnade
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute und auch ir habe und
                        kauffmanschaft und die iren in die nehstkünfftigen frankfurter vastenmesse
                        und wider darausz mit geleyte <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle, also <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sie oder die iren darümb czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden oder aber
                        den ewren <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und des bergern, daz sie und daz ir
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch ewr lande, herschaft und gepyte
                        sicher geleytet werden, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und
                        biten auch des ewr gnedig, <expan>vschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener.
                            <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Mathie
                            <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan> anno xvi<hi rend="sup">mo</hi>
<expan>cuil<ex>ibet</ex></expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan>. <app>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>officialib<ex>us</ex></expan> sic:
                                    <expan>Wen<ex>n</ex></expan> sie oder die iren darümb czu euch
                                kumen und des begern, daz ir sie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch
                                ewr gepiete, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ir czu geleiten habt,
                                sicher geleyten wöllet, als etc.; das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                                etc. </note>
</app></ab></div>
</div></body>
</text>
